[DhtmlXQ_comment15]And this was the move that was played by GM Liu. It was quite an innovation in those days as it now allows red to play R1=2 and targets black's weakness on the board mericilessly. A very strategically oriented board.[/DhtmlXQ_comment15]
[DhtmlXQ_comment16]Master Huang: As seen from the diagram, black's only flaw is the side elephant, thereby causing much disharmony to his formation. This would become a fatal flaw later![/DhtmlXQ_comment16]
